{"id":5998,"date":"2012-09-07T11:55:23","date_gmt":"2012-09-07T15:55:23","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=5998"},"modified":"2023-07-06T15:46:43","modified_gmt":"2023-07-06T11:46:43","slug":"parable-prophet-warning-army","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/07\/parable-prophet-warning-army\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Parables: The Prophet is like warning of an enemy"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Verily, the parable of what Allah has sent to me is that of a man who came to his people and he said, &#8216;O people! I have seen an army with my own eyes, and I give you a clear warning that you should flee to safety!&#8217; A group among his people obeyed and fled to a place of safety. A group among them denied him and remained in their place. When morning came, the army attacked and destroyed them. That is the parable of one who obeys me and follows what I have been sent with, and one who disobeys me and denies the truth I have been sent with.&#8221;<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7283, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2283<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0<\/strong><\/em>(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0645\u064e\u062b\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a \u0648\u064e\u0645\u064e\u062b\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e\u064